list.abstract: Final（英 [ˈfaɪnl]，美 [ˈfaɪnl]），英语单词，作形容词为最后的；最终的；决定性的。作名词为决赛；课程终结考试；主调音。短语搭配有final decision（最后决定）。例句为“Proofread, or edit your final draft.（校对或编辑您的最终草稿。）” Final形容词类近义词有ultimate，crucial等。名词类近义词有shoot-off，fight-off。
final（[英]['faɪnl][美][ˈfaɪnəl]），英文单词。 adj.最后的，最终的; 决定性的; 不可更改的。 n.结局; 决赛; 期末考试; （报纸的）末版。

yingyinNormal.en: A desperate mission. Our final hope.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一项绝地任务，我们最后的希望。

yingyinNormal.en: As night falls the mighty Lan Cang River is host to one final ritual.
yingyinNormal.zh: 夜幕降临，澜沧江迎来了最后的仪式。

yingyinNormal.en: Rangers. The last components of our one versatile ship in orbit, the Endurance, our final expedition.
yingyinNormal.zh: 漫游者。这是在轨道上一艘多功能船，永恒号的最后一个组件，我们最后的远征。

yingyinNormal.en: You have the finest engineers in all the world. My final counsel to you is that you put them to work. Construct the Latin's siege engine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 您有着世界上最好的机械师，我最后的忠告就是重用他们，建造那个拉丁人说的攻城机器。

yingyinNormal.en: There's always one. There's just time for some final rehearsals. Organizing this whole operation, including over 2,000 performers, is Mason Hung.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总会有一个苏格兰人。这是最后的彩排了。这场包括两千多位演员的活动就是由洪忠兴组织举办的。

yingyinNormal.en: The final key! It's being broadcast.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后一把钥匙！在直播。

yingyinNormal.en: She got an "A-" On the French final.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她法语期末考只得了个A-。

yingyinNormal.en: Well. Surprise final act. Best of luck.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧。没想到最后会是这个结果。

yingyinNormal.en: Attention, all initiates report for final testing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请注意，所有新成员，来最终测验报道。

yingyinNormal.en: And to think I've been worrying about my Potions final.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可我却在为魔药学期末考试担心。

yingyinNormal.en: I really hope this tree hugger crap isn't on the final.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真希望最后不要让我拥抱大自然什么的。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, number one: in matters of physics, I have the final say. In matters of neuroscience, you have the final say. Unless I disagree.
yingyinNormal.zh: 规则一：跟物理有关的，我有最终决定权。跟神经科学有关的，你有最终决定权。除非我不同意。

yingyinNormal.en: Have the final numbers on my desk by Tuesday. If you say so sir.
yingyinNormal.zh: 星期二以前，把正确数字放在我桌上。照你的意思做吧。

yingyinNormal.en: But in the wars final days, one Autobot ship escaped the battle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但在战争结束之前，一艘汽车人战舰逃离了战场。

yingyinNormal.en: You never did escape. But here we are again, for one final round.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你从未逃离，但我们再次相逢，来到最后一局。

yingyinNormal.en: So good news! The divorce is final. I signed the papers this a.m.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好消息，我已经离婚了，我今天早上签了文件。

yingyinNormal.en: I see you left this final question blank. What is your occupation?
yingyinNormal.zh: 您最后一栏没有填，您做什么职业？

yingyinNormal.en: Would you look at this dump? He hated us. This is his final revenge.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看看这个猪窝？他痛恨我们！这是他最终的报复！

yingyinNormal.en: Wow. Rachel, you're a real special lady, but my divorce isn't final yet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瑞秋，你是个很特别的女性，但我的离婚还没办完。

yingyinNormal.en: I appreciate your coming here in person. Especially during the, final rush.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我感谢你亲自过来，尤其在这最后冲刺阶段。
